<title>USA: Capstone says halts securities sale.</title>
<headline>Capstone says halts securities sale.</headline>
<dateline>IRVING, Texas 1997-04-16</dateline>
<text>
<p>Capstone Pharmacy Services Inc said Wednesday that, in connection with its announcement of a proposed merger with Beverly Enterprise Inc's pharmacy unit, it has suspended sale of securities.</p>
<p>Capstone said the move is pursuant to its two current shelf registration statements on Form S-3 effective as of the opening of business today in order to file supplemental disclosure materials pursuant to federal securities law requirements.</p>
